headline: CoStar Group to Present at RBC Capital Markets 2024 Global TIMT Conference
summary: WASHINGTON, November 13, 2024--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, and analytics in the property markets, will present at this year’s RBC Capital Markets 2024 Global TIMT Conference. CFO Chris Lown and Head of Investor Relations Rich Simonelli will participate in a fireside chat on Wednesday, November 20, 2024, at 3:20 p.m. ET.
